**Since 5.0**, you can now find those values in a dedicated `Enum`: [`org.hibernate.boot.SchemaAutoTooling`][1] (enhanced with value `NONE` since 5.2).

Or even better, **since 5.1**, you can also use the [`org.hibernate.tool.schema.Action`][2] `Enum` which combines JPA 2 and &quot;legacy&quot; Hibernate DDL actions.

